text: Þis <sy> to miclangrafe on tenet on eastan <middel>.
Þonne þonan suþ andlang dices up on fileþa þonan on stræte on eala wihing pyt þonan andlang weges þonan oþþa <ea>.
Þonne þonan &lang dices on haman <fleot> west &lang ea on middel gewæd & þonan west on seolcing fleot east &lang fleotes on haggan fleot &lang hacggan fleotes toemnes middelbyrum.
Þis is þaraVIsulunga boc æt Miclangrafe þe Eadmund cing gebocode Ælfstane his þegne on ece yrfe.
